item.title: Kubeflow
item.description: Context Google Kubeflow team organised a Kubeflow doc sprint in July 2019. A doc sprint is like a hackathon for docs. Over the course of three days, participants developed tutorials and fixed documentation bugs. Participation I participated on Day 2 and helped document an overview topic on using Jupyter notebooks in Kubeflow. Links Github PR: https://github.com/kubeflow/website/pull/914
